{"tid":1781934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沈旭暉正式與CCTVB藝人撐Popo活動割蓆","createTime":"2019-12-13T14:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T18:02:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ae38358999751612db7ecfdd6878ba977e198352","tid":1781934,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7O8q3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7O8q3O.jpg&h=bb64356c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【關公】有網友問，我係咪有出席一個「愛比暴力強」警察活動，咁我一頭霧水。原來有心人，喺呢張相後面塊backdrop，見到我個簽名，叫我不如提一提，咁我一定遵命。<br />\n<br />\n感謝網友提醒，Er Sir背後呢塊，應該係警察公共關係科辦公室既舊backdrop，過去幾年，任何一個人去過佢地office，都會被邀請簽名，而大家知道謝振中係我中學師兄(...)，當年好出名既童軍，我附近既簽名有好多名人，好似羅永聰，或者尹光。我去佢地office，大概已經係兩年前既事，佢地介紹一輪做PR，簽名應該係當時既。<br />\n<br />\n講真，我同好多警察本來好熟，特別係senior，因為我曾經同佢地學堂講過國際關係課程，仲要全英文（當時佢地英文真係好好的）。但係6月之後，就無去過，而佢地，恐怕都唔會再請我去了；呢個活動，自然都唔關我事，謝師兄唔blacklist我，已經偷笑。見到一段段關係破壞，係好唏噓，但至於警隊入面有無白警，我保證肯定有，只係，真係唔多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2903737979660333/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2903737979660333%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6tTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=d0de0f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2903737979660333/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"010eba586f6040324f4ea274508a0c3593049653","tid":1781934,"uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"啲人咁眼利，沈旭暉嗰簽名喺邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6978d0db4d74e4469124dcf51dbf80e923228b2","tid":1781934,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"但至於警隊入面有無白警，我保證肯定有，只係，真係唔多。<br />\n<br />\n好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223171b58382363815c7e9c60bf735a38debad6a","tid":1781934,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780483c55785c1d781e441bf98c537423108d874","tid":1781934,"uid":135740,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae38358999751612db7ecfdd6878ba977e198352","tid":1781934,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7O8q3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7O8q3O.jpg&h=bb64356c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【關公】有網友問，我係咪有出席一個「愛比暴力強」警察活動，咁我一頭霧水。原來有心人，喺呢張相後面塊backdrop，見到我個簽名，叫我不如提一提，咁我一定遵命。<br />\n<br />\n感謝網友提醒，Er Sir背後呢塊，應該係警察公共關係科辦公室既舊backdrop，過去幾年，任何一個人去過佢地office，都會被邀請簽名，而大家知道謝振中係我中學師兄(...)，當年好出名既童軍，我附近既簽名有好多名人，好似羅永聰，或者尹光。我去佢地office，大概已經係兩年前既事，佢地介紹一輪做PR，簽名應該係當時既。<br />\n<br />\n講真，我同好多警察本來好熟，特別係senior，因為我曾經同佢地學堂講過國際關係課程，仲要全英文（當時佢地英文真係好好的）。但係6月之後，就無去過，而佢地，恐怕都唔會再請我去了；呢個活動，自然都唔關我事，謝師兄唔blacklist我，已經偷笑。見到一段段關係破壞，係好唏噓，但至於警隊入面有無白警，我保證肯定有，只係，真係唔多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2903737979660333/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2903737979660333%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6tTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=d0de0f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2903737979660333/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"佢地英文好? 唔撚係丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c9caa4736f97e4356acec423999d0606ae6cfc","tid":1781934,"uid":165683,"like":0,"disl